metadata.name: Instinto Maternal
metadata.description:
Motherâ€™s Instinct is a collaborative project between digital artist Lolita and Virgen Maria, 
It consists of an image that explore the convergence of spirituality and technology. Through the use of digital 3D techniques, timeless concepts such as bonding and empathy are redefined in a modern context. 
The connection between mother and child, and the powerful force of birth, whether it is in life or artistic creation, is honoured in the series, creating a timeless love story for a modern audience.
